Class PrototypeFrame

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.qos.frame.Frame
      org.cougaar.core.qos.frame.PrototypeFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, NotPersistable, VariableEvaluator, UniqueObject
public class PrototypeFrame
extends Frame

This extension to Frame is the runtime representation of a prototype. It's main job at runtime is to hold non-static default values (static defaults are code-generated into constants) and to process Path slot values.
